"Prometheus" --> "node_exporter" : scrape :9100
"Prometheus" --> "Blackbox Exporter" : probe
"Blackbox Exporter" --> "Web服务" : HTTP/TCP
"Spring Boot" --> "Prometheus" : HTTP API
